Project Summary:
Nirvana v2: Electric Boogaloo is the research name for DirectSyscallDetector's
return-provenance technique for raw and gadgeted direct syscalls. The project
demonstrates instrumentation-callback-based direct syscall detection, live
syscall return-address cataloging from ntdll.dll and win32u.dll, and
PHNT-backed syscall signature printing from recovered syscall IDs.

